	printf("\n  WHAT CONSTELLATIONS CAN AND CANNOT PROCESS gLAB IN VERSION 6 (FIRST MULTICONSTELLATION VERSION)?\n\n");
	printf("       SPP mode: Process all constellations.\n\n");
